bio.openEndedText:
Thank you for checking out our vehicles!

 I am Justin Gregory I own Drive Easy Rentals LLC a new up and coming Turo host growing a fleet of vehicles striving for the best customer service & always being accommodating to needs & wants of our clients
 We try to stick with eye catching cars luxury economical vehicles so you get the looks but also the MPG for your trips thank you for your time & I look forward to doing business with you!

Hello, my name is Gregory, and welcome to Turo!

With Turo, I focus on providing an affordable, reliable, and economical car for anyone who needs a vehicle.

My vehicles have instant booking turned on, and I do a contactless key exchange. This means I won't actually be there when you pick up the vehicle. This gives you a more convenient and flexible booking and rental experience.

My cars aren’t perfect. They have wear and
tear, so if you are looking for a perfect rental car that is in showroom floor quality then unfortunately my cars are not for you. But, if you are looking for a professionally maintained, reliable, and clean car then my vehicles are perfect for you!

Though my cars have wear and tear they are meticulously maintained. They are cleaned and disinfected between every single rental and they will get you to where you need to go safely.

If you are looking for a host you can count on, look no further than right here!

Im Eric, and I aim to treat everybody well and fair.
I’ve been a host since Nov. 2023 and I’ve had some ups and downs that I’ve learned from.
 I know that this is many people first time on 
Turo. I understand that so you are in good hands with me.
 I deal with cars on a regular basis, doing rentals and outside of rentals. 
I can tint, paint rims, fix saggy headliners. paint brake calibers, and so forth. 
I have 15 cars that I rent out. I have 4 Hondas 2019 & up.
 I have 3 beautiful Camry's, a van, a Lexus, a Jeep, 3 Hyundai Elantras and a Mazda.
 Everyday, I am doing maintenance to my cars.
 All day I am making sure the tires are inflated to proper specifications, alignments, proper thread depths, oil changes, and checking all fluids because all of these things are important. 
If my Honda needs work, me or my team member take it to the Honda Dealership.
If a Camry needs work, its going to the Toyota Dealership, you dig?
The Lexus is serviced by Lexus.
And so forth.
Last but not least, cleaning. 
Sanitizing and Cleaning is important to me. 
All of these factors are very costly. 
That's why I have to charge what I am worth.
 I appreciate you ahead of time if you deciding to shop with me.
 If you want a quality experience then shop with me. 
I have AirTags for my keys. 
Please don't take them off. 
These keys cost $500 because the dealership has to program them in order to work PROPERLY. 
I have options to prepay for fuel in there so you can just drop the car off when your trip is finished and we will refuel for you.
Also, unlimited mileage options for people who need to go up north, down south, mid-west and even the west coast.
I try to NOT deal with people who are not responsible.
 I'd rather keep my cars parked.
 I appreciate everyone but I know for a fact that all money isn't good. 
If there are any issues with your reservations or the car that you reserved, communication is key.
 I have cars to swap you out if need be. 
Many people find fault in me but do not communicate it to me and then go blast me on reviews. 
This is the times we are living in. 
Well, I am here to restore humanity lol... 
Have a good day.

And leave a review even if I suck,,,

WHY RENT FROM ME?

⛽️With gas prices 📈 ,my Trax and yes even the Jeep, all have gas mileage that will make you want to keep them forever 😂
🏠Every Turo booking helps this Navy Vet get one step closer to purchasing a home 🤝
🎖I’m a Turo Power Host
⚓️I’ve been told by multiple renters that my customer service, professionalism and attention to detail is unrivaled by other hosts
⚡ INSTANT booking on every car (no need to wait for approval)!  
🕙 Cars available for pick-up/drop off 24/7
⏳  Last minute bookings available!
🛑 We never cancel on you. We understand how important your travel plans are to you and we are committed to helping you see them through. Because of this commitment, we will not initiate a cancellation on our end

It’s my goal to make every trip as easy and seamless as possible. All pickups and drop-offs have a contactless option to ensure renters feel safe.

🧼 Each vehicle is cleaned and sanitized before and after each trip
🧰 Service appointments are performed regularly by the dealership because we want you to have a reliable and safe travel option
💲Repeat customers and customers who refer family and friends receive discounts on future trips 🙏🏽

Please reach out prior to booking if you have any questions or special requests (336) 348-7443.

Thank you and I look forward to accommodating your next travel experience! 🚗🚙🏎

bio.employment: Every day from ground up building an ENGLISH EMPIRE in rental vehicles and sweat hoods only to remind you of an ENGLISH experience.
bio.openEndedText: Hi guys, I’m your host Mr. English and thanks for stopping by my page of ENGLISH MOTOS. Here you’ll find my 1st & hopefully several more selective well maintained trending colorful rentals. I too have rented many of vehicles and thought how I could service customers in such ways as I hoped to be serviced. So here I am, first handed, giving you a well cleaned and safe rental with many features to enjoy your trip. All I ask is you follow the TURO guidelines and treat this vehicle as if you were expecting to rent again and would like to receive it in the same shape and conditions as you have when the keys were given. Please no smoking as it’s a rental violation and a violation to others who don’t smoke.  I too am human and tend to forget policies put in place to keep order but now that I have the chance to run a business I see what hard work it takes to remind myself of the importance that’s needed to keep customers safe & happy. So help me, help you, help others to making this a win win experience.

I’m Terence a new resident here in NC, I’m originally from NY and moved here two years ago to start a new life outside of corporate America…. I’m an AirBNB host and Landlord which somehow led me down the Turo path.  Here on Turo I’ve managed to marry my love of being of service to people and my fascination with cars.  Over the past 10 months I’ve managed to amass 10 cars and have developed all the processes needed to support this business well.  I’m here at your service and I’m willing to accommodate all requests that follow the terms of service.
